FRP Tunnel plugin for OPNsense

Provides a GUI for managing FRP (Fast Reverse Proxy) client and server.
Designed for cross-border tunnel stability with built-in network tuning
options (BBR, MSS clamping).

Features:
- FRP Client (frpc) with full TOML v0.60+ configuration
- FRP Server (frps) with web dashboard support
- Proxy management (tcp, udp, http, https, stcp, xtcp, etc.)
- Network tuning: TCP BBR, MSS clamping (integrated in Client settings)
- Cross-border optimizations: tcpMux, heartbeat, TLS, connection pooling

WWW: https://github.com/fatedier/frp
